&kp AT     &kp GRAVE           &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp SEMICOLON          &kp COMMA                         &none          &kp RIGHT_SHIFT  &kp RIGHT_GUI     &kp RCTRL          &kp RIGHT_ALT  &kp ESCAPE
